Class OrdinaryItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • stock.Item
      • stock.OrdinaryItem

  • public class OrdinaryItem
extends Item
    This class extends Item, and defines all of the abstract methods in terms of an ordinary non-perishable item.
    Author:
    Daniel Field, Allen Basic
